{"tid":1669040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦：「欲求文明之幸福，不得不經文明之痛苦。」","createTime":"2019-10-22T10:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T08:25:23.000Z","uid":263197,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"269a2c85fe39170a27f99b4bb44cc7c8acd5a38c","tid":1669040,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:23:25.000Z","msg":"吳璟儁：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n梁天琦：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「我意思係，如果有任何雞蛋被人打爛嘅話，可能佢唔願意參與你嘅革命，係咪佢無選擇權嘅呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「佢有選擇權，佢絕對有選擇權。但係一場咁大嘅社會衝突，要完全做到對其他人無影響，係無可能嘅事。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「唔願意參與革命嘅人，如果最後被犧牲嘅話，你嘅感覺會係點？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「難受，絕對難受。但係有一句說話我覺得係好啱。<span style=\"color: orange;\">『欲求文明之幸福，不得不經文明之痛苦。』</span>咁所以⋯⋯社會變革係一定有動盪。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n梁天琦接受無綫訪問（新東補選票站現場）<br />\n2016年2月29日 (影片中4:32開始）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/G835tHyrW0Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FG835tHyrW0Y&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DUwDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=bd79fc1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/G835tHyrW0Y</a><br />\n<br />\n「欲求文明之幸福，不得不經文明之痛苦。」來自 《十月圍城》"},{"pid":"2fe8c671fcbd17a8ef48bc95b2f470fd1f9f923f","tid":1669040,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:24:38.000Z","msg":"抗爭一定有沙石只能說服同路人<br />\n對文宣無幫助"},{"pid":"e3329c395b47d3c95f7ee7c56bd80928f8b58f6e","tid":1669040,"uid":124277,"like":1,"dislike":30,"score":-29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:25:04.000Z","msg":"撻句文言文就以為自已好有point<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c81fc